    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce is beginning to thicken, add your <strong>haddock bites </strong>(unevenly sized haddock bites? Chop any larger ones into bite-sized pieces!) to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
