    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the haddock is cooking, wash your<strong> spinach</strong> then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the<strong> wilted spinach</strong> under <strong>cold running water </strong>until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can</p><p>Add the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Thai green haddock & green bean curry</strong></p>",
